snippet: During a 15-hour trip, Gov. Andrew M. Cuomo met with political figures including Benjamin Netanyahu and offered emotional support to Jews in Israel and New York....

headline.main: In Season Openers, the Red Bulls Rally and New York City F.C. Falls Short
headline.print_headline: Red Bulls Rally to Win Season Opener

lead_paragraph: During a 15-hour trip, Gov. Andrew M. Cuomo met with political figures including Benjamin Netanyahu and offered emotional support to Jews in Israel and New York.
